Reasoning: The paper deals with the construction of hopsets, which are used in various computational settings such as dynamic graph algorithms, distributed computing, and the streaming model. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories related to these areas. Specifically, cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) are likely candidates as they are directly related to the construction and use of hopsets. cs.Distributed (Distributed Computing) is also a possibility as hopsets are used in this area. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) are less likely but still possible as hopsets have applications in these areas as well.
